title: Donald Trump Has a Man Bun
text:

Donald Trump is known for his comb over hair style, but now he is rockin' a new look! While his look may be Photoshopped, here are three celebrities that can actually pull off the man bun. Do you love or hate the man bun? Teresa Strasser wants to know, so share your thoughts in the comments below. Copyright 2015 Scripps Media, Inc. All rights reserved.
